DESCRIPTION
------------------------------------------------
This is the mote connected to the EGC board. The EGC will
transmit data to the mote using UART communication. 

EGC and mote need to be connected with two cables, GND and 
Data.

An scenario description is explained on the document "Wireless Crane
Event-Triggered Control" by Aitor Hernandez, Faisal Altaf and
Jose Araujo
